OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary
OL,4,CCholwill
OL,6,FMary Cholwill, Age 100, Auxiliary
OL,7,FTerritorial Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 1 October 2024
OL,11,FJoining the ATS at 17 in 1941 with her
OL,12,Fparents' consent, Mary Cholwill was
OL,13,Fworking as a telephonist and plotter
OL,14,Fin Dorset when D-Day took place.
OL,16,FAfter her training at Aldermaston in
OL,17,FBerkshire she was attached to the
OL,18,FRoyal Artillery Searchlight Regiment.
