OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary
OL,4,CCholwill
OL,6,F"They said you are too young for the
OL,7,FRoyal Artillery with the guns, " Mrs
OL,8,FCholwill said.
OL,10,F"So I was on the battery headquarters
OL,11,Fthat controlled all the sites with
OL,12,Fsearchlights on."
OL,14,FAccording to the National Army Museum
OL,15,Fwebsite: "Searchlights were an
OL,16,Fimportant component of Britain's
OL,17,Fdefence against the German bombing
OL,18,Fcampaign during World War Two.
OL,26,@oD@_P~
