OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary
OL,4,CCholwill
OL,6,F"Searchlights were used to locate and
OL,7,Filluminate enemy bombers, providing
OL,8,Ftargets for anti-aircraft gun
OL,9,Fbatteries. With increasing numbers of
OL,10,Fmale soldiers serving overseas, in
OL,11,FNorth Africa and the Far East, women
OL,12,Ffrom the ATS were drafted in to
OL,13,Foperate searchlights from 1941."
OL,15,FMrs Cholwill said: "Also with the
OL,16,Fsearchlights, if there was a bomber
OL,17,Fcoming home from Germany that was
OL,18,Fdamaged and they were having a job to
OL,19,Ffind their way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
