OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mary
OL,4,CCholwill
OL,6,FThis was close to Tarrant Rushton
OL,7,Fwhich played a key role in Operation
OL,8,FOverlord. The first Allied troops flew
OL,9,Fin gliders from the airfield there and
OL,10,Fwere dropped behind enemy lines hours
OL,11,Fbefore the beach landings.
OL,13,FThey were a unit from the Oxfordshire
OL,14,F& Buckinghamshire Light Infantry.
OL,16,FMrs Cholwill added: "More often than
OL,17,Fnot when you're posted you're not told
OL,18,Fwhere you're being posted to until you
OL,19,Fget there.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
